  Scenario: Count with excluded id
    When I send a POST request to "/api/v1/en_GB/batch-action/count" with body:
      """
      {
        "type": "product_edit",
        "filter": {
          "ids": {
            "list": [
              "@product_id_1@"
            ],
            "included": false
          }
        }
      }
      """
    Then the response status code should be 200
    And the JSON node count should exist

